F

FifoDistributedBiConsumer<T> - Interface in com.simukappu.coherence.distributed.fifo
FunctionalInterface extends BiConsumer to distributed processing as First in, first out.
This consumer calls putIfAbsent-like method to coherence cache with a key and then call process method only when the entry is first in.
We have to call this interface with a stream including coherence cache name to use as the key set for distributed processing
FifoDistributedBiFunction<T,R> - Interface in com.simukappu.coherence.distributed.fifo
FunctionalInterface extends BiFunction to distributed processing as First in, first out.
This function calls putIfAbsent-like method to coherence cache with a key and then call process method only when the entry is first in.
We have to call this interface with a stream including coherence cache name to use as the key set for distributed processing
FifoDistributedBiProcessor<T> - Interface in com.simukappu.coherence.distributed.fifo
Interface to distributed processing as First in, first out.
This interface is to be extended by FunctionalInterface with two arguments like BiConsumer or BiFunction.
FifoDistributedConsumer<T> - Class in com.simukappu.coherence.distributed.fifo
